snippet.title: Designing for AI with Zade Kaylani
snippet.description:
https://landle.world?utm_source=Matt&utm_medium=youtube&utm_campaign=replit-builders
https://replit.com?utm_source=Matt&utm_medium=youtube&utm_campaign=replit-builders

Replit designer Zade reveals how to design agentic AI experiences and use AI tools without losing your creative edge

Key Points:
00:28 Meet Zade: From astronautical engineering to designing Replit Agent
05:11 Building Landl: Creating internal tools with AI to solve design problems
12:00 Finding creative inspiration in traffic lights, Minecraft, and SpongeBob
19:00 Why chat interfaces aren't always the right model for AI agents
23:00 Simplification without dumbing down: Designing for power and accessibility
28:25 Essential tip: Don't outsource the human touch to AI

#AI #Design #Replit #ProductDesign #UserExperience #AIAgents #VibeCoding #TechCareers #CreativeTech #DeveloperTools

How do you balance using AI tools to accelerate your workflow while preserving your unique creative perspective? Share your experiences in the comments.
